{"1":[[0,129,"I'm Jax Carter."],[183,396,"My MMA dad never claimed me."],[421,567,"And neither did his family."],[613,671,"To them,"],[717,909,"I'm just the bastard he had"],[909,975,"with the maid."],[1059,1172,"I train with three masters"],[1172,1343,"in secret, so that one day,"],[1372,1622,"I can prove myself and give my mother"],[1622,1751,"the life she deserves."],[3649,3770,"You okay, princess?"],[4696,4850,"That's the first time I've been able"],[4850,4925,"to touch him."],[5492,5680,"I finally got this."],[6243,6435,"Looks like he just got hit by a bus."],[6660,6719,"At your age,"],[6719,6831,"I was already running laps"],[6831,6956,"around the top killers in the game."],[8324,8429,"Can't carry 'em?"],[8612,8725,"Jax has to wear 'em."],[8946,9067,"1200 pounds."],[9067,9171,"You wear 'em day and night."],[9171,9275,"Even when you sleep."],[9305,9471,"Walking, breathing, existing."],[9488,9592,"That's how you get strong."],[9617,9768,"You take them off before we say,"],[9809,9947,"you're no longer our disciple."],[10018,10122,"No more training."],[10143,10260,"No more martial arts."],[10289,10406,"No shot at power."],[10497,10581,"And your mother?"],[10581,10731,"Stays a janitor forever."],[11094,11211,"Pressure makes champions."],[11215,11365,"It's the only rule that matters."],[11411,11473,"Can I go?"],[11594,11644,"Fine."],[11724,11782,"But remember,"],[11782,11924,"nobody can know we train you."],[12295,12445,"Little shit actually tagged me."],[12470,12558,"Kid ain't normal."],[12570,12771,"If he's so strong, then why the cuffs?"],[12771,12833,"Aren't you afraid"],[12833,12917,"you're gonna break him?"],[13088,13192,"Praise breeds ego."],[13204,13321,"Ego gets you choked out."],[13384,13480,"He wants to tap into his"],[13480,13571,"Godweight Build."],[13592,13788,"He needs pressure, not compliments."],[13797,13984,"Come on, Godweight Build?"],[14043,14134,"That's gym folklore."],[14134,14222,"No one's ever seen it."],[14222,14351,"The old trainers used to say"],[14351,14435,"there was a few of 'em,"],[14439,14531,"one in a million."],[14564,14639,"Fighters with bodies"],[14639,14760,"that defies physics."],[14760,14910,"They called it the Godweight Build"],[14919,14998,"because it wasn't designed"],[14998,15148,"for anything but fighting."],[15169,15236,"He has it."],[15244,15365,"He's just not ready to use it."],[15536,15611,"Yet."],[15832,15961,"I've been wearing these cuffs"],[15961,16045,"for a week now."],[16120,16341,"I wonder how much stronger I've gotten."],[17108,17175,"Uncle."],[17250,17325,"Father."],[17354,17496,"I will prove you wrong."],[17947,18034,"Nothing."],[18109,18284,"I'm still so weak."]],"2":[[16,108,"Jax, get out here!"],[175,233,"Where have you been?"],[279,442,"Why did you hit your cousin Troy?"],[479,525,"I just-"],[550,688,"You humiliated us."],[700,763,"Again."],[763,859,"You need to apologize"],[859,971,"to your uncle and your cousin."],[1034,1101,"We're going to beg"],[1101,1176,"for their forgiveness."],[1176,1351,"You don't understand, Troy-"],[1351,1493,"No backtalk!"],[1526,1589,"Do you want them to"],[1589,1718,"kick us out completely?"],[2961,3032,"Stop it!"],[3044,3128,"That's enough!"],[3128,3294,"Then, clean up the mess, maid."],[3524,3570,"You slap me"],[3570,3682,"like you're a tough guy, huh?"],[3699,3782,"Now you get wrecked."],[3995,4191,"Keep playing victim."],[4208,4341,"I barely tapped you,"],[4354,4496,"and now your head's all wrapped up"],[4496,4608,"like you just got back"],[4608,4708,"from a warzone."],[4783,4934,"You think this is funny, Jax?"],[5117,5267,"He spat on my mom yesterday."],[5301,5380,"What would you have done?"],[5380,5451,"Your mom?"],[5459,5634,"She's a house rat in janitor scrubs."],[5634,5734,"Say that again."],[5834,5985,"Apologize to your cousin,"],[5985,6085,"and to your uncle."],[6085,6131,"Mom."],[6218,6331,"He started this."],[6368,6427,"Why should I--"],[6890,6981,"Please."],[7374,7449,"See, Frank?"],[7482,7553,"He's handled."],[7653,7778,"Which hand did he hit you with?"],[7836,7903,"His right."],[7974,8024,"Break it."],[8245,8341,"Frank, no!"],[8379,8450,"Please."],[8462,8587,"Hurt me if you have to."],[8612,8687,"Not him!"],[8742,8812,"Do it."],[9067,9209,"If they see the cuffs,"],[9259,9342,"it's over."],[9384,9471,"No more training."],[9542,9705,"No more second chances."],[9926,9984,"They'll know"],[9984,10126,"I've been hiding everything."]],"3":[[0,112,"See, you little bastard?"],[266,362,"Nobody gives a shit."],[442,508,"Wait!"],[855,1034,"The Crucible recruitment combine"],[1034,1096,"is tomorrow."],[1134,1276,"We all know the Crucible"],[1276,1401,"is the most elite"],[1426,1639,"training group in UCF history."],[1668,1801,"They take one fighter"],[1801,1922,"every five years,"],[1922,2168,"and every single one"],[2202,2344,"has gone on to be a champion."],[2394,2531,"I've already submitted our roster."],[2619,2723,"Jax included."],[2798,2982,"If he doesn't show, we're out."],[3015,3119,"Disqualified."],[3140,3215,"Dad, come on."],[3215,3324,"You're really gonna let him off the-"],[3803,3995,"If that combine wasn't tomorrow,"],[3995,4129,"I would cripple you"],[4191,4258,"right here."],[4379,4437,"For today,"],[4512,4612,"you get to keep your hand."],[4713,4808,"After the combine,"],[4896,4967,"it's mine."],[5246,5388,"Get the fuck out of my face."]],"4":[[342,383,"Blake,"],[479,525,"thank you."],[592,633,"Go on."],[646,729,"Thank your brother."],[1639,1847,"Mmm, he's wearing weights."],[1935,2064,"He must be training hard."],[2143,2231,"Don't thank me yet."],[2260,2364,"Show up tomorrow."],[2423,2652,"Blow them away."],[2677,2865,"Only way Uncle Frank backs off."],[2957,3019,"One shot."],[3161,3286,"Make it count."],[4245,4408,"That's Camden Carter,"],[4437,4521,"my father."],[4558,4675,"Hard to even call him that."],[4696,4900,"Walks right past us like we're ghosts."],[4909,5055,"Like we never existed."],[5697,5818,"Let's pack our things tonight."],[5872,5951,"We can disappear."],[6006,6097,"Just you and me."],[6101,6231,"Everything I'm doing"],[6231,6448,"is to give you and me a better life."],[6519,6606,"Tomorrow's our shot."],[6735,6902,"And no one is taking this hand"],[6902,6944,"from me."],[8433,8521,"Who's the street rat?"],[8566,8692,"Carter Clan's bastard."],[8712,8808,"The janitor's son."],[8821,8913,"Heard they keep them locked"],[8913,8983,"in the basement."],[8983,9042,"Right?"],[9134,9209,"Today,"],[9263,9396,"I'll prove myself."]],"5":[[283,437,"The Crucible installed"],[437,575,"2,000-pound"],[629,809,"unbreakable steel dummies"],[825,1076,"outside every gym in this region."],[1092,1322,"They say that anyone who can crack one"],[1347,1413,"would get"],[1438,1760,"immediate access to the Crucible."],[1801,2047,"The dummy outside our gym was split"],[2047,2231,"clean down the middle yesterday."],[2277,2439,"Nobody knows who did it."],[2473,2677,"Could it be the same dummy?"],[3557,3724,"But I didn't even leave a scratch."],[3757,3916,"There's no way."],[3953,4054,"Unless-"],[4054,4154,"Hey, Camden."],[4195,4325,"I heard your little bastard"],[4325,4446,"is on the roster today."],[4471,4575,"I cannot wait to see"],[4575,4700,"which maggot is him."],[4833,4929,"Let me guess, dad."],[4988,5080,"Is he that one?"],[5121,5188,"Yo!"],[5209,5296,"The Crucible"],[5338,5492,"is a proving ground."],[5501,5764,"Not a pity parade for secret kids."],[5851,5964,"Yo Camden!"],[5989,6068,"You sure"],[6110,6227,"he's your own blood?"],[6260,6348,"Because I don't know, man."],[6352,6418,"Maybe your maid"],[6418,6548,"fucked your dog by mistake and-"],[6919,7036,"How the hell"],[7044,7198,"am I supposed to stand a chance"],[7198,7303,"with these still on?"],[7328,7428,"If I took them off,"],[7465,7578,"just for this,"],[7636,7745,"I might actually win."],[8299,8408,"Welcome to the Crucible."],[8458,8591,"First trial begins now."]],"6":[[863,992,"First test is Strength."],[1021,1159,"Each fighter would strap in and"],[1159,1334,"pull that plane as far as they can."],[1363,1480,"Most distance wins."],[1514,1630,"He's gonna get hurt."],[1643,1780,"He shouldn't be out there."],[1797,1906,"He chose this."],[1906,2043,"He's not like them."],[2060,2118,"Well,"],[2193,2314,"he better try to be."],[2427,2506,"I'll go first!"],[2840,2990,"Our first contestant is Drake,"],[2990,3111,"from Iron King."],[5976,6051,"Six feet."],[6072,6122,"Oh!"],[6181,6235,"Come on."],[6423,6523,"Watch how it's done."],[6577,6652,"Up next,"],[6677,6852,"Troy, from Carter Clan."],[7640,7724,"Seven feet."],[7928,7962,"Yes!"],[8003,8062,"Yes!"],[8308,8433,"Even I had to dig deep"],[8487,8579,"to move that thing."],[8612,8742,"That means you're fucking toast."],[8783,8896,"After today, those hands of yours"],[8896,8975,"won't be safe."],[9000,9109,"My hands don't answer to you."],[9125,9317,"Up next is Rick,"],[9355,9480,"from Iron King."],[9576,9642,"Eight feet."],[9684,9818,"Let's go!"],[9834,9880,"Wooh!"],[9880,9964,"Up next"],[9989,10139,"is Blake, from Carter Clan."],[10155,10247,"That's Blake Carter."],[10281,10422,"Strongest in the Carter Clan."],[10502,10664,"Top-tier strength in all of L.A."]],"7":[[1130,1893,"Carter Clan!"],[2631,2723,"Fourteen feet."],[2723,2831,"Yes!"],[2877,2919,"Yes!"],[2940,3094,"That's real Carter blood."],[3795,3895,"Don't worry too much."],[5926,5985,"Let's go!"],[5989,6031,"Let's go!"],[6031,6110,"Come on, come on! - Yeah!"],[6110,6177,"Let's go, D, you got this!"],[6177,6264,"Come on, Dante, you got it!"],[6264,6335,"Yeah!"],[6881,7011,"He's doing it with one hand!"],[7040,7111,"Let's go! - Let's go, baby!"],[7111,7203,"That's what I'm talking about!"],[7203,7286,"First place, baby!"],[7286,7349,"Can't touch this!"],[7369,7432,"Can't touch this."],[8737,8808,"Finish line."],[8812,8917,"Let's go, baby!"],[8921,9025,"Yeah!"],[9025,9154,"That's true talent. - Let's go!"],[9154,9196,"Yeah!"],[9196,9438,"Iron King MMA is now first place."],[9446,9534,"Let's go!"],[9534,9634,"Iron King! - Yeah!"],[9655,9738,"Iron King!"],[9759,9826,"How the hell - Iron King!"],[9826,9951,"is he that strong? - Iron King!"],[9972,10114,"My uncle snuck me"],[10114,10260,"into the Crucible years ago."],[10297,10510,"I've been training in secret ever since."],[10535,10664,"I just hope that's all he's got."],[10673,10814,"If his fight game is as good"],[10814,10881,"as his strength,"],[10910,11015,"Carter Clan's in trouble."],[11044,11140,"Anyone left?"],[11186,11294,"Our gym's got one more."],[11528,11669,"They're really sending the help"],[11669,11749,"to help them out?"],[11774,11949,"Man, Carter Clan got soft."],[11970,12116,"Ten bucks says he pulls a hamstring"],[12116,12237,"just tying the harness."],[12466,12545,"Come on, bro."],[12566,12683,"You're not freezing up, are you?"],[12825,12983,"Please take him out."],[13000,13088,"He's not ready."],[13117,13246,"He asked for this."],[13555,13688,"1200 pounds."],[13717,13830,"You wear 'em day and night."],[13830,13913,"Even when you sleep."],[13980,14139,"1200 pounds on my body."],[14185,14289,"If I take them off,"],[14305,14414,"I lose everything."],[14456,14539,"No training."],[14564,14660,"No future."],[14685,14869,"No way to lift my mom out of this hell."],[14989,15098,"So that's why"],[15115,15331,"I have to win."]],"8":[[79,175,"Look at him, man."],[191,312,"Moving like a zombie."],[387,504,"Walking Dead-ass."],[508,684,"No idea why Blake signed you up."],[717,788,"This is over!"],[1434,1526,"Show 'em what you got, kid."],[4500,4596,"Right on cue."],[4604,4763,"Trash stays trash."],[4917,5050,"1200 pounds for the cuffs"],[5050,5176,"and a thousand for the plane rig?"],[5180,5276,"He still should have been able to"],[5276,5321,"crush it."],[5321,5426,"Oh, right."],[5434,5784,"I swapped out his cuffs for yours."],[5784,5839,"What? - What?"],[5839,5972,"Your cuffs are pushing"],[5997,6177,"three thousand pounds, easy."],[6235,6348,"Why doesn't he just remove them?"],[6364,6498,"Because we told him to keep 'em on."],[6581,6698,"And because he listens."],[7077,7336,"I can't give up."],[9476,9567,"Mmm, okay."],[9580,9726,"I did not see that coming."],[9797,9922,"That's it!"],[10539,10606,"Loser!"],[10635,10689,"No, no, no."],[10689,10748,"No way, this guy. - I can' take him"],[10748,10798,"No way, this guy. - seriously."],[10798,10848,"I can't take him-"],[10865,10998,"Loser! - Oh my!"],[11052,11152,"Official mark."],[11161,11227,"Five feet."],[11290,11373,"Last place."],[11407,11490,"All this time for a guy"],[11490,11674,"who can't even finish the first test."],[11682,11836,"Straight up embarrassing!"],[12253,12362,"That's a man?"],[12474,12625,"I promise you, mom."],[12666,12962,"This isn't over yet."]],"9":[[4,91,"Next trial,"],[125,196,"Speed."],[329,408,"The car behind"],[408,588,"will start half a second after you do,"],[633,784,"at 35 miles per hour."],[1105,1172,"Fall behind?"],[1409,1472,"You're out."],[1626,1664,"Oh."],[1718,1780,"Come on."],[1801,1943,"Fastest time ranks highest."],[1947,2031,"I'll start us off."],[2077,2164,"Watch and learn."],[3949,4054,"18 seconds."],[4250,4320,"Not bad."],[5125,5288,"Iron King team in the lead."],[5309,5522,"Next up, Blake, from Carter Clan."],[5534,5580,"Let's go, baby."],[5580,5626,"Let's go, Blake."],[6681,6781,"11 seconds."],[6781,6865,"Yes! - Yeah."],[6865,6923,"Yes!"],[6977,7057,"Yes!"],[7098,7219,"They're gonna get the shit"],[7219,7261,"ahead of us."],[7269,7357,"That's it, Blake! - Nice."],[7365,7411,"That's it!"],[7432,7469,"That's it!"],[7469,7549,"Yes!"],[7757,7849,"Come on, go, D!"],[7849,7937,"Come on!"],[7937,7974,"Bring it on!"],[7974,8091,"Let's go, yeah! - Let's go!"],[8587,8737,"Yeah!"],[8737,8833,"Yes!"],[8846,9234,"Iron King!"],[9284,9376,"10 seconds."],[9426,9496,"First place."],[9530,9626,"Yeah! - Wooh!"],[9626,9722,"That's what I'm talking about!"],[9809,9968,"How is he first again?"],[9976,10197,"First in Strength, and now in Speed."],[10372,10472,"Last participant."],[10514,10581,"Jax Carter."],[10789,10881,"Yo, yo, time to see"],[10881,11002,"if this charity case can run in"],[11002,11073,"a straight line."],[11094,11186,"Only competition"],[11186,11282,"he's winning today"],[11340,11444,"is the fastest bitch"],[11444,11557,"who's gonna start crying"],[11574,11678,"after he loses."],[11682,11853,"You took last in Strength."],[11853,11974,"Might as well sit this one out."],[11982,12099,"Save us the embarrassment."],[12479,12741,"1200 pounds."],[12846,12971,"But I can't give up."],[13042,13329,"This time, I will prove myself worthy."]],"10":[[1555,1726,"I can't be last again."],[1739,1956,"I'm tired of being at the bottom."],[1997,2085,"You disgust me."],[2093,2227,"You filthy-"],[2231,2323,"Leave her alone!"],[2585,2831,"You'll never be one of us, bastard."],[3019,3157,"His mom cleaned this toilet."],[3169,3332,"Troy, he smells like a dog"],[3332,3499,"ate shit then died."],[3520,3607,"Stop it!"],[3962,4112,"He's running faster than the car!"],[4112,4241,"How's the bastard doing that?"],[4250,4341,"That's not speed."],[4433,4537,"That's something else."],[5492,5676,"I'm going to win."]],"11":[[154,250,"You're trash, man!"],[258,358,"Just fall already!"],[379,521,"The cuffs, they're still on."],[529,583,"There's no way"],[583,679,"he can sustain this speed."],[684,796,"But why doesn't he just take them off?"],[809,913,"Razor told him"],[913,1034,"to wear them all the time."],[1034,1238,"Even when he sleeps or we'll disown him!"],[1735,1901,"What did you say, boy?"],[2014,2248,"Know your place, bastard."],[2335,2565,"Time to teach him a lesson, ha!"],[2744,2873,"Not again."],[3148,3261,"Oh, yes!"],[3328,3370,"Yes!"],[3520,3649,"Oh!"],[3691,3870,"Hope he liked the taste of sand."],[5088,5171,"Oh! - No!"],[5280,5405,"Fucking lucky bastard."],[5747,5914,"Why is his arm so heavy?"],[6614,6715,"As expected."],[6723,6865,"Jax Carter has failed."],[6936,7015,"Fuck, I knew it."],[7040,7132,"Look at this fucking guy."],[7136,7223,"He's never gonna beat me."],[7223,7298,"He's never gonna fucking beat me."],[7298,7394,"Why does the Carter Clan"],[7394,7532,"even allow clowns like this"],[7532,7645,"into the combine?"],[7720,7791,"It's weak."],[8696,8846,"I'm sorry, mom."],[8933,9134,"I promise I won't let you down again."]],"12":[[145,225,"Final event,"],[266,342,"Cage Trial."],[450,508,"Even those who"],[508,646,"failed the last two rounds"],[646,763,"still have a shot here."],[775,963,"This round decides everything."],[1146,1213,"Silas,"],[1234,1343,"I got a suggestion."],[1351,1472,"King of the Hill."],[1488,1710,"My son against everybody!"],[1722,1868,"Lambs to the slaughter."],[1893,2002,"Yeah! - Wooh!"],[2002,2135,"Let's go. - Let's go."],[2515,2644,"None of you are making it through."],[2656,2827,"But if anyone's feeling brave,"],[3011,3103,"step on up."],[3215,3269,"I'll go."],[3470,3603,"Go show 'em what Carter blood"],[3603,3716,"can really do, son."],[3728,3795,"Yeah, let's go!"],[3828,3933,"Let's go! - Yeah!"],[4120,4266,"Are you sure you want to do this?"],[4283,4466,"Or you just here to die pretty?"],[4504,4688,"I'm here to shut your damn mouth."],[5910,5955,"Let's go!"],[7394,7457,"No!"],[7461,7524,"Come on."],[7632,7720,"Yeah!"],[7862,8024,"Are you afraid to die?"],[8287,8375,"Get off of him!"],[8450,8525,"C'mon."],[8525,8658,"Is this all you got?"],[8700,8767,"Frank, sit him down."],[8792,8979,"Send up your bastard, Camden."],[9004,9150,"Might as well mop the floor"],[9150,9305,"with your entire bloodline."],[9430,9534,"When this is over,"],[9576,9693,"we absorb your gym."],[9705,9884,"And then I'll make all the calls."],[9922,10068,"Wooh. - Yeah."],[10185,10268,"Let's go."],[10289,10372,"Come on!"],[10418,10556,"This is what happens"],[10606,10739,"when you let the help"],[10764,10902,"breed with royalty."],[10944,11048,"This kid,"],[11073,11186,"he's not a fighter."],[11340,11503,"He's a genetic fuckup."],[11974,12053,"Dante,"],[12107,12299,"this is where you fall."]],"13":[[4,166,"Oh, so now he wants to fight?"],[175,362,"Somebody call 911 now"],[362,475,"so we can get ahead of this shit show."],[567,729,"You're gonna humiliate us again,"],[729,771,"dude?"],[771,884,"You don't belong in there."],[892,1017,"You weren't raised to fight."],[1042,1205,"You were raised to clean up after us."],[1217,1288,"Jax,"],[1347,1451,"don't do this."],[1497,1589,"You made your point."],[1593,1647,"You don't need to"],[1647,1755,"prove yourself to them."],[1810,1964,"It's not about proving"],[1981,2097,"anything anymore, Mom."],[2823,2977,"They've been stepping on you"],[3007,3228,"my whole life."],[3386,3474,"No more."],[4971,5088,"Bastard's got weights?"],[5092,5209,"Now he's 10 pounds lighter."],[7403,7545,"This is prima metal."],[7599,7703,"This has gotta a weigh"],[7703,7887,"at least fifteen hundred pounds."],[8016,8158,"Who the hell is this kid?"],[8195,8304,"I'm Jax Carter,"],[8354,8441,"of Carter Clan."],[8533,8662,"And I'm here to fight you."],[8917,9096,"You think you can go toe-to-toe with me."],[9284,9446,"Fight my ass, you little bastard."]],"14":[[709,892,"That's my boy!"],[1117,1230,"Our boy's still holding back."],[1230,1322,"That punch had weight,"],[1322,1388,"but he still pulled it"],[1388,1463,"at the last second."],[1463,1564,"He's not reckless."],[1609,1751,"Jax isn't made to kill."],[1876,1997,"He's made for control."],[2102,2223,"So this is the strength"],[2223,2314,"he's been hiding."],[2385,2515,"Crush him, son!"],[2515,2635,"Break him in half!"],[2644,2740,"Come on, Dante!"],[2740,2794,"Come on!"],[2806,2873,"Come on!"],[2873,2952,"I'll admit it."],[3036,3228,"I underestimated you, bastard."],[3228,3365,"But that strength of yours?"],[3399,3595,"It won't change a damn thing!"],[3641,3745,"You and your mother"],[3791,3883,"will always be"],[3974,4162,"gutter trash."],[4166,4450,"Keep her name out of your mouth!"],[7282,7524,"That's my boy, yeah!"],[7615,7711,"Son!"],[7711,7849,"That little brother of mine."],[7849,7941,"He's different."],[7995,8095,"He's the future."],[8108,8199,"Son!"],[8262,8362,"You okay?"],[8404,8483,"Talk to me!"],[8500,8633,"Don't scare me, son."],[8746,9117,"I swear to God, I'll end you!"]],"15":[[4,442,"I swear to God, I'll end you!"],[446,625,"You think you can fuck with my son"],[625,738,"and there's no price?"],[763,1021,"I will kill you right now!"],[1055,1180,"Right here!"],[1217,1263,"Stop!"],[1430,1584,"You're a real piece of shit."],[1630,1785,"You've got no shame, do you?"],[1876,1981,"What, you get beat?"],[1989,2147,"You think you're gonna hit a kid?"],[2160,2344,"Well, why don't you hit me instead?"],[2748,2902,"Get out of my way, Camden!"],[2927,3182,"I'm gonna tear his goddamn head off!"],[3182,3290,"Not today!"],[3328,3495,"Because Jax Carter"],[3507,3670,"is my son!"],[3874,3966,"And you don't get to"],[3966,4137,"lay a finger on him."],[4633,4842,"Then, I'll deal with you first!"],[4946,5067,"Jax, watch out!"],[5100,5146,"Move!"],[7795,7874,"Coach Mercer."],[8028,8116,"Silas."],[8437,8483,"Brother."],[8525,8625,"You came in person."]],"16":[[25,150,"Jax Carter."],[233,300,"You fought like"],[300,462,"no one we've seen in years."],[554,633,"But,"],[688,850,"we can't accept you into the Crucible."],[955,1163,"We have a morality clause."],[1205,1359,"The Crucible can't take in"],[1359,1539,"fighters born in sin."],[1564,1697,"We set a standard."],[1739,1972,"Your very bloodline violates it."],[1981,2060,"It's horseshit!"],[2064,2118,"That's it!"],[2143,2227,"That's it!"],[2243,2481,"You can't cheat blood, bastard!"],[2485,2627,"He's not an outsider!"],[2665,2765,"He's my son."],[2765,2836,"And that means"],[2836,2961,"he's got Carter blood."],[2969,3019,"Period!"],[3032,3153,"You were married"],[3153,3282,"when you fathered him."],[3324,3511,"His mother was a maid"],[3511,3645,"who seduced you."],[3678,3787,"You hid them."],[3807,3933,"Lied about them."],[3941,4141,"This isn't about strength."],[4145,4287,"It's about honor."],[4300,4596,"The Crucible can't take on sinners!"],[4600,4675,"You mean to tell me that"],[4675,4783,"you're gonna turn away"],[4796,5000,"the greatest fighter we've seen in,"],[5025,5234,"I don't know how long, ever"],[5292,5438,"because of his background?"],[5501,5559,"Vaughn."],[5638,5834,"I challenge this decision."],[5905,6076,"You're just protecting your family."],[6126,6239,"You're not looking out"],[6239,6398,"for the future of the Crucible."],[6464,6660,"You're looking out for your nephew."],[6669,6790,"And that's a conflict of interest."],[6806,7032,"And you, you know it."]],"17":[[33,271,"To admit a bastard into the Crucible"],[291,396,"would make a mockery"],[396,613,"of everything we stand for."],[642,1021,"This is a gym that produces warriors."],[1046,1251,"Our fighters must be perfect,"],[1284,1655,"mind, body, and legacy."],[1718,1805,"Such a shame."],[1860,1964,"The kid had hands."],[2002,2110,"Rules are rules."],[2156,2252,"I didn't realize"],[2252,2444,"Iron King Gym's been in bed"],[2444,2623,"with the Crucible this entire time."],[2660,2773,"Carter Clan."],[2840,2982,"You're disqualified."],[3032,3086,"Dip!"],[3132,3182,"Now!"],[3328,3403,"He won"],[3470,3645,"fair and square."],[3712,3837,"Shut your mouth, Camden."],[3870,4095,"The Crucible Director is on his way."],[4120,4320,"And if he finds you still standing here,"],[4337,4558,"he'll wipe you off the mat himself."],[4600,4746,"Nothing he hates more"],[4746,4900,"than a rule breaker."],[4900,5038,"You are not the director,"],[5042,5150,"so why the hell"],[5180,5280,"should we listen to you?"],[5359,5568,"Because your life means nothing."],[5597,5780,"When our director arrives,"],[5780,5922,"he won't even look at you"],[5922,6089,"while taking your life away."],[6147,6285,"So, go ahead."],[6302,6439,"Stick around."],[6464,6614,"But don't blame me"],[6614,6781,"when this ends with your name"],[6781,6931,"on a body bag."]],"18":[[325,433,"You held your ground."],[454,571,"That's all that matters."],[608,742,"You did what real fighters do."],[742,829,"You didn't fold."],[913,1051,"Now let's see if they're dumb enough"],[1051,1126,"to swing on us."],[1155,1426,"Who the hell do you think you are?"],[1463,1626,"You talking to us that way?"],[1626,1701,"You must have a"],[1714,1826,"death wish or something."],[1864,1926,"Nah."],[1989,2127,"I think you're asking for a funeral."],[2152,2260,"Get the fuck out of here"],[2260,2402,"and take that bastard with you"],[2402,2581,"before the Director arrives."],[2627,2736,"Last chance."],[2786,2894,"Take the kid and leave,"],[2907,3061,"or get buried with him."],[3707,3883,"Man still thinks he's in his prime."],[3958,4024,"You,"],[4062,4170,"you wanna go next?"],[4896,4967,"Wait, is that-"],[5017,5171,"Oh my God, that's Hud Sumner."],[5217,5367,"Director of the Crucible."],[5914,6122,"Director Sumner, so glad you're here."],[6143,6231,"We, uh..."],[6477,6585,"Founders of the Cage."],[6702,6802,"Allow me to apologize"],[6802,7002,"on behalf of my colleague here."],[7311,7374,"Apparently,"],[7374,7494,"he's forgotten his manners."],[7515,7745,"Wow, turns out my masters are"],[7745,7966,"actually the founders of the Cage?"]],"19":[[125,283,"Director Sumner, what are you doing?"],[308,462,"No way you're taking their side?"],[467,579,"You stupid fuck."],[646,713,"These three are the"],[713,846,"founders of the Cage."],[875,963,"The original architects"],[971,1138,"of everything the Crucible is built on."],[1142,1384,"Everything the UFC is built on."],[1422,1576,"Decades ago, they disappeared."],[1589,1701,"Became ghost."],[1726,1922,"But every champion you've ever admired,"],[1922,2085,"every technique you've mastered,"],[2139,2210,"came from them."],[2248,2310,"Vaughn."],[2369,2590,"You owe your rank to these three."],[2615,2715,"And instead of honoring"],[2715,2777,"their legacy,"],[2777,2936,"you try to throw out their own student?"],[2961,3057,"This kid came here"],[3057,3207,"out of respect of the institution"],[3207,3349,"that you disgraced."],[3382,3482,"You tried to disqualify him"],[3482,3649,"over who his fucking parents are?"],[3687,3845,"I, I didn't know."],[3845,3912,"No!"],[3953,4074,"You didn't give a shit."],[4129,4212,"I am sorry."],[4254,4366,"For all of this."],[4446,4587,"I too was your student."],[4646,4717,"It's because of you"],[4717,4842,"the Crucibles rose to power"],[4842,4942,"in the first place."],[4967,5105,"We're not here for apologies."],[5163,5246,"We're here for him."],[5451,5568,"He doesn't need to take a test."],[5568,5613,"He's in."],[5926,6097,"I'll take him as my student right now."],[6218,6385,"You're not qualified to teach him."],[6414,6498,"He's our student."],[6573,6731,"Your people called him trash."],[6731,6835,"But by seniority,"],[6835,6977,"he's the student of the founders"],[6977,7057,"of the Crucible."],[7082,7286,"So, how should you address him?"],[8395,8521,"He's giving him the fist."],[8591,8754,"No one's ever gotten that from Hud."],[8888,9017,"Crucible Director Jax,"],[9180,9242,"please"],[9288,9392,"accept my apology."],[9392,9526,"Wait, did I just become"],[9526,9647,"the Director of the Crucible?"],[9647,10039,"Director Jax!"]],"20":[[4,91,"You actually thought that"],[91,208,"you could get away with"],[212,321,"sneaking in your nephew?"],[387,496,"Into the Crucible?"],[513,625,"Train him in secret?"],[679,867,"And rig the whole combine"],[867,1088,"in Iron King's favor?"],[1259,1438,"All results from the Iron King MMA"],[1438,1522,"are now voided."],[1539,1593,"What?"],[1605,1676,"What the hell?"],[1722,1822,"Yeah!"],[2110,2281,"Effective immediately."],[2289,2435,"No one from the Iron King's Gym"],[2435,2681,"will ever join the Crucible ever again."],[2752,2844,"And Vaughn Mercer,"],[2915,2994,"you're expelled."],[3090,3153,"What?"],[3211,3420,"Director Sumner, wait, please."],[3428,3541,"Give me another chance."],[3541,3578,"I-"],[3578,3691,"Get them out of my sight."],[3716,3816,"Wait, wait, wait!"],[3887,3933,"Not me."],[3933,4054,"I, I've been loyal."],[4095,4258,"I helped build this place."],[4283,4346,"Wait, don't,"],[4358,4500,"don't I at least deserve to know"],[4500,4662,"who broke the dummy?"],[4808,4934,"Whoever shattered the dummy"],[4934,5184,"will be granted immediate entry."],[5246,5372,"That dummy was forged with"],[5372,5513,"composite prima steel."],[5518,5593,"Even us,"],[5593,5705,"the founders of the Crucible,"],[5705,5793,"couldn't crack it."],[5855,5951,"Whoever did,"],[6018,6122,"they ain't normal."],[6227,6314,"I know who did it."]],"21":[[70,150,"I know who did it."],[554,679,"You said you might know"],[679,775,"who broke the dummy?"],[863,909,"Do you?"],[1001,1063,"Where is it?"],[1134,1201,"It was supposed to be"],[1201,1301,"the final test today."],[1347,1447,"I'll take you to it."],[2027,2147,"Only an MMA genius"],[2147,2218,"with freakish strength"],[2218,2385,"can even move one of these dummies,"],[2427,2531,"let alone crack it."],[2585,2786,"It's the same as the one I cracked open."],[2873,2961,"You know who did it?"],[5046,5113,"Whoa!"],[5296,5442,"Holy shit."]],"22":[[37,75,"Hud."],[329,396,"Before we go,"],[521,654,"I wanna take my mom home first."],[717,800,"Make things right."],[850,917,"It's fine."],[963,1038,"I'll stay in L.A."],[1038,1126,"a few more days."],[1163,1242,"And when you're ready,"],[1284,1388,"we ride back together,"],[1472,1547,"to the Crucible."],[1568,1609,"Alright."],[1630,1714,"Director Jax."],[2152,2231,"Let's go home."],[2673,2727,"Mom."],[2932,3007,"We did it."],[3194,3311,"You did it, son."],[3570,3616,"Come on."],[3670,3745,"Let's go home."],[3978,4091,"It's been a day."],[4462,4617,"You little bastard!"],[4796,4929,"You destroyed my family's gym."],[5042,5130,"I'll pay you back"],[5209,5305,"a hundredfold!"],[5472,5734,"You got dumped by the Crucible."],[5768,5951,"And we lost everything."],[5980,6239,"We cannot let this shit slide!"],[6289,6406,"The Crucible hasn't touched"],[6406,6506,"the East coast yet."],[6806,6944,"We'll go East."],[7007,7157,"Link up with their enemies."],[7173,7303,"And when we're ready,"],[7323,7557,"we burn the whole thing down."],[7599,7691,"Jax Carter,"],[7745,7853,"I'm coming for you."],[7949,8179,"And your fucking family!"]],"23":[[533,617,"Coach Taggert."],[900,1017,"I'll be straight with you."],[1088,1288,"You asked me to join years ago."],[1309,1497,"I should've said yes then."],[1522,1647,"But I'm saying it now."],[1722,1830,"I'm in."],[1968,2039,"Get out."],[2277,2377,"I brought you intel."],[2435,2590,"The boss said get out."],[2748,2973,"Inside info on the Crucible."],[3365,3415,"Good."],[3553,3624,"Very good."],[3691,3795,"With your intel"],[3795,3945,"and Black Tide's secret weapon,"],[3978,4308,"we will crush them all at the UCF East."],[4350,4471,"Two weeks from now,"],[4471,4729,"the Crucible will not know what hit them."],[4729,4950,"But there's one fighter"],[4950,5084,"you should know about."],[5188,5313,"Name's Jax Carter."],[5580,5689,"Where did you get that photo?"],[5768,5885,"The kids' social media."],[5930,6151,"That's his mom, Maria Carter."],[6181,6281,"Mops floors"],[6281,6460,"at the Carter Clan gym in L.A."],[6498,6631,"It's not Maria Carter."],[6731,6873,"That's my daughter."],[6873,6986,"That's Sarah Taggert."]],"24":[[12,166,"That's my daughter."],[166,258,"That's Sarah Taggert!"],[371,550,"20 years ago, she ran off."],[621,875,"I had no idea she ended up"],[875,1096,"with the Carter Clan bastards."],[1134,1238,"Are you sure it's her?"],[1238,1355,"Don't insult me."],[1401,1551,"A man knows his own blood!"],[1559,1680,"Then you should know,"],[1776,1935,"her life's been hell."],[2014,2193,"They treat her like a maid."],[2206,2364,"No respect."],[2385,2506,"They forced her"],[2506,2681,"to have Camden Carter's kid."],[2681,2736,"What?"],[2798,2998,"I'm gonna destroy that family!"],[3086,3219,"Then let's go now."],[3228,3407,"And we don't just fight Carter Clan,"],[3432,3595,"we erase them."],[3707,3891,"I'm gonna bring one of my pets."]],"25":[[679,825,"Hey, congrats man."],[884,963,"Director of the Crucible,"],[963,1172,"that's some Carter Clan shit."],[2577,2669,"It's go time."],[2740,2902,"L.A. ain't ready for this."],[4037,4220,"We're here to fucking crush."]],"26":[[29,91,"Jax."],[179,250,"I was wrong"],[312,383,"about you."],[454,525,"I'm sorry."],[525,713,"You treated my mom like shit"],[729,813,"for years."],[884,992,"You let them beat her,"],[1030,1121,"humiliate her!"],[1188,1305,"And you just stood there"],[1355,1443,"and watched!"],[1822,1868,"I-"],[1868,1935,"I what?"],[1956,2027,"Jax."],[2118,2185,"Not here."],[2252,2318,"Not tonight."],[2982,3044,"What the hell?"],[3958,4112,"And who the fuck do you think you are?"],[4112,4212,"They came out of nowhere."],[4212,4337,"We didn't stand a chance."],[4379,4491,"Don't even know where they're from."],[4533,4637,"Not nowhere."],[4667,4775,"East Coast."],[4800,4904,"Black Tide."],[4942,5005,"What do you want?"],[5005,5105,"Hand over Sarah."],[5117,5296,"And I'll leave you corpses intact."],[5296,5338,"Sarah?"],[5384,5434,"Yeah."],[5455,5534,"She's one of us."],[5568,5714,"A member of Black Tide."],[5734,5889,"And she's in your gym right now."]],"27":[[25,158,"A member of Black Tide."],[175,354,"And she's in your gym right now."],[429,575,"There's no one in this gym"],[575,704,"connected to Black Tide."],[704,846,"You've got the wrong address."],[900,963,"Where's mom?"],[1021,1142,"You hand Sarah over,"],[1172,1272,"you get roughed up."],[1272,1384,"If you don't,"],[1434,1630,"we paint this floor with your blood."],[1639,1793,"Hey, you think you can come in here"],[1793,1906,"and push us around?"],[4517,4650,"Enough!"]],"28":[[12,141,"Enough!"],[383,513,"So you're the one, huh?"],[567,679,"You knocked her up and then"],[679,813,"you left her to rot."],[4233,4300,"Oh!"],[4325,4458,"There's someone here in this gym"],[4458,4562,"with real spine?"],[4633,4700,"Okay."],[4825,4925,"Let's see what you got."],[4954,5013,"Back it up."]],"29":[[41,166,"We don't even know why you're here."],[191,417,"Now get the hell out of our gym."],[754,855,"You wanna play hero?"],[925,1059,"Fuck around and find out."],[3244,3349,"Come on, pretty boy!"],[3370,3465,"That all you got?"],[3536,3716,"L.A. fighters got flashed,"],[3716,3812,"no backbone."],[3883,4029,"Y'all soft out here."],[4116,4212,"Say that again."],[5997,6101,"He's getting wrecked."],[6122,6256,"He can't take them!"]],"30":[[667,825,"Is this the best L.A."],[825,938,"has to offer?"],[1201,1251,"No wonder"],[1251,1451,"we've been stopping you for years."],[1797,1868,"We're not done."],[3599,3724,"Stay down, kid."],[5167,5242,"Round two."],[5305,5376,"Let's go."],[5442,5509,"Hey!"],[5538,5663,"Cut this shit!"],[5801,5976,"Coach Taggert?"]],"31":[[12,191,"I didn't bring you here to play games."],[191,367,"I brought you here to finish them!"],[379,583,"Start busting skulls!"],[1155,1472,"Ready to die, Mr. Director?"],[1472,1589,"After what you pulled,"],[1589,1718,"The Crucible cut us off."],[1735,1906,"That means our gym is dead."],[1906,2060,"And if our gym is dead,"],[2060,2344,"so is your whole goddamn family!"],[2344,2448,"You cowards."],[2456,2623,"You got smoked and crawled into bed"],[2623,2694,"with the enemy?"],[2719,2827,"Fucking traitors."],[2861,2940,"All of you!"],[2982,3048,"And you."],[3107,3290,"You're the one who ruined my family."],[3303,3461,"You took my only daughter,"],[3470,3666,"forced her into a life of servitude,"],[3682,3924,"made her carry your bastard child?"],[3945,4058,"What's he talking about?"],[4241,4308,"Your mother."],[4487,4642,"Her name isn't Maria Carter."],[4859,5025,"It's Sarah Taggert."],[5201,5280,"My daughter."],[5321,5401,"My heart."],[5422,5538,"My pride and joy."],[5563,5659,"And he took her."],[5659,5772,"Why'd she come to us then?"],[5784,5980,"Why take a maid job if she had family?"]],"32":[[37,166,"Because I had no one left"],[166,258,"to protect me."],[333,542,"And no one who believed in me."],[734,900,"Why'd she never tell me that?"],[980,1092,"You humiliated her."],[1109,1201,"You used her."],[1234,1313,"Then you hid her away"],[1313,1463,"like a dirty little secret."],[1463,1647,"And then you just walked away!"],[1647,1743,"It's not like that."],[1772,2035,"When Blake's mother died, I was a mess."],[2060,2177,"Maria, she helped me."],[2189,2285,"We got close."],[2323,2494,"I wanted to make things official, but,"],[2535,2585,"but I-"],[2585,2656,"But what?"],[2861,2982,"But I was weak."],[3044,3190,"My family, this gym,"],[3190,3311,"they didn't approve of her."],[3311,3478,"They thought she was beneath me,"],[3478,3570,"so I lied."],[3582,3712,"I kept her quiet."],[3712,3841,"And when she got pregnant,"],[3912,4024,"I didn't defend her."],[4124,4358,"I just let them treat her like dirt."],[4358,4517,"You let them call her a whore."],[4604,4767,"My whole life!"],[4863,4963,"And I stayed."],[5096,5217,"For you, mi hijito."],[5230,5413,"He broke my heart, but you,"],[5451,5630,"you became my reason to live."]],"33":[[16,191,"You became my reason to live."],[621,721,"You're not forgiven."],[834,905,"Not yet."],[1009,1067,"I know."],[1067,1117,"All right."],[1117,1305,"This is all very sweet and sentimental"],[1305,1384,"and everything."],[1384,1693,"But once a bastard, always a bastard."],[1747,1901,"Today, Taggert finishes"],[1901,2014,"what should have been handled"],[2014,2122,"20 years ago."],[2143,2277,"You should have been aborted"],[2277,2398,"a long time ago."],[2431,2819,"So today, I'm gonna kill you first."],[3290,3357,"Jax!"],[3357,3407,"Get him!"],[3774,3899,"She can fight?"],[4191,4279,"Whoa, Mom."],[4375,4500,"It's been a long time."],[4579,4642,"Dad."]],"34":[[237,396,"It's good to see you still got it."],[462,575,"After all these years,"],[629,792,"you haven't forgotten what I taught you."],[867,992,"You haven't changed either, Dad."],[1101,1201,"Still heartless."],[1292,1372,"Heartless?"],[1413,1463,"Me?"],[1547,1705,"These people humiliated you."],[1768,1956,"Forced you to have their bastard child."],[1989,2114,"And I'm the heartless one?"],[2135,2239,"Yeah, right."],[2281,2473,"I have no beef with anyone here."],[2489,2702,"Even if you don't, I do."],[2752,2894,"They took you away from me."],[2915,3011,"And they're gonna pay."],[3048,3186,"Leave, Dad."],[3303,3461,"They deserve what's coming to them."],[3816,3908,"20 years,"],[3933,4004,"gone."],[4087,4233,"Father and daughter together again,"],[4233,4491,"and the first thing we do is square off"],[4529,4637,"like enemies?"],[4767,4888,"Come back with me, Sarah."],[5000,5246,"Compete for the UCF East Championship"],[5246,5317,"in two weeks."],[5326,5551,"Together, we can win it all."]],"35":[[54,133,"Say yes."],[191,262,"And I'll consider"],[262,383,"sparing all of these people"],[383,533,"that you care so much about."],[563,675,"The ones that treated you like"],[709,792,"dog shit."],[846,1017,"You want to know why I left?"],[1134,1222,"Because you never showed me"],[1222,1368,"an ounce of affection."],[1484,1668,"You didn't raise a daughter."],[1680,1810,"You sharpened a weapon."],[1901,1964,"Fight!"],[1972,2043,"Fight!"],[2052,2131,"Fight!"],[2202,2314,"Always for you."],[2314,2410,"Never for me."],[2419,2556,"You were born for the big time."],[2573,2777,"Raised to win and take power."],[2827,2977,"That's all the world respects."],[3007,3090,"In a few years,"],[3090,3178,"you and I could run"],[3178,3290,"the Crucible together."],[3370,3536,"Ever since I left Black Tide,"],[3561,3774,"I've lived in anonymity."],[3795,3945,"I swore I'd never fight again."],[4108,4287,"After the shit you pulled today,"],[4404,4571,"I have even less reason to go back."],[4934,5067,"Get out, Dad!"],[5334,5388,"Fine."],[5609,5714,"But don't blame me."],[5789,5976,"'Cause shit's about to get real, girl."]],"36":[[1597,1672,"Go!"],[1685,1760,"Come on!"],[2923,2977,"Mom!"],[3432,3532,"You're my daughter."],[3570,3657,"You forget"],[3678,3807,"who taught you everything."],[3878,4033,"But not everything I know."],[4062,4154,"How the hell do you think"],[4154,4241,"you're gonna beat me?"],[4320,4450,"Let my mom go!"],[4567,4717,"Little bastard Jax,"],[4729,4909,"I'll give you one more look at her, boy."],[4950,5038,"Make it good."],[5084,5251,"'Cause it's gonna be your last."]],"37":[[120,216,"Director Hud."],[346,492,"So nice to see you again."],[492,613,"Not director anymore."],[667,855,"Your grandson here, Jax Carter,"],[855,1030,"he's the new director of the Crucible."],[1076,1176,"And you touch him,"],[1230,1292,"you're declaring war"],[1292,1409,"on the entire Crucible."],[1434,1618,"A little bastard, like him?"],[1618,1739,"He's gonna run the Crucible?"],[1876,2002,"Shit must be running downhill"],[2002,2135,"like a runaway train."],[2135,2243,"It's not your business."],[2344,2406,"Vaughn."],[2598,2706,"Get these people out of here."],[2940,3161,"I'm not with the Crucible anymore."],[3178,3374,"I'm Black Tide now."],[3395,3582,"You can't order me around."],[3770,3933,"What will it take for you to let this go?"],[4020,4166,"Damn it, now that Hud's here,"],[4166,4333,"I can't touch the Carter Clan."],[4366,4462,"Not today."],[4542,4629,"You wanna protect them?"],[4629,4679,"Fine."],[4688,4904,"The UCF East is in two weeks."],[4904,4996,"We're hosting."],[5046,5380,"I win, the Crucible gets out of L.A."],[5388,5551,"the Midwest and the West."],[5580,5764,"Then, the Carter Clan"],[5784,5918,"fights under my banner."],[5926,6110,"And they do as I say."],[6143,6306,"You really think that you can take over"],[6306,6452,"a whole damn country like that?"],[6473,6581,"And what if you lose?"],[6669,6785,"Then it's up to you."],[6873,6956,"If you lose,"],[7069,7207,"you give my mother her freedom."],[7570,7645,"Her peace."]],"38":[[12,216,"You really think you can win,"],[237,362,"you little bastard?"],[400,517,"You're out of your depth."],[558,654,"You just don't get it."],[688,809,"In the last ten years,"],[809,905,"L.A.'s put together"],[905,1159,"maybe five wins. Total."],[1180,1297,"And that's being generous."],[1313,1459,"You're chasing a fantasy, man."],[1459,1564,"On fight day,"],[1576,1814,"if you manage to tag me even once,"],[1847,1997,"I'll consider it my loss."],[1997,2085,"And make sure"],[2085,2277,"every last Carter Clan scumbag"],[2277,2373,"signs up."],[2385,2540,"I wanna break them all"],[2590,2669,"personally."],[2802,2873,"Let's go."],[3119,3140,"Get up."],[3140,3165,"No."],[3182,3203,"No."],[3236,3294,"Get off!"],[3294,3349,"Mom."],[3611,3732,"Let my mom go!"],[3862,3924,"Get off of me."],[3928,3983,"Get off of me."],[3983,4037,"Mom!"],[4170,4233,"Mom!"],[4600,4667,"Damn it!"],[4783,4913,"Those two weren't even the best"],[4913,5050,"that Black Tide has."],[5055,5138,"They went through us"],[5138,5296,"like we were sparring dummies."],[5334,5597,"When we go to UCF East in two weeks,"],[5597,5784,"what the hell are we gonna do?"],[5805,6006,"Why am I still such a goddamn weakling?"],[6018,6110,"Director Jax,"],[6135,6231,"the founders are asking for you."],[6272,6427,"UCF East is no joke."],[6523,6631,"I'm going back to the Crucible"],[6631,6727,"to make arrangements."],[6735,6861,"Come by whenever you're ready."],[6886,7107,"The resources we have, it's yours."]],"39":[[350,433,"I don't know how the hell"],[433,525,"I'm supposed to beat them."],[571,600,"I mean,"],[600,767,"Black Tide's a whole different animal."],[767,880,"Yeah, because they're juiced"],[880,975,"to the gills."],[1009,1138,"They're running enhanced stacks."],[1138,1263,"They're not your regular roids."],[1263,1551,"Designer-level bio-cocktails."],[1568,1668,"It gives them more power"],[1668,1805,"than any guy's ever trained them."],[1826,1922,"That's why you can't fight them"],[1922,2022,"like a regular fighter."],[2039,2139,"You have to tap in what's already"],[2139,2227,"inside you."],[2256,2344,"The Godweight Build."],[2344,2394,"Mm-hmm."],[2419,2590,"Half of it's already awakened in you."],[2615,2698,"We've seen it."],[2740,3003,"But if you want any chance at UCF East,"],[3003,3215,"you have to fully unlock it."],[3228,3357,"There's only one way to do it."],[3407,3461,"Let me guess."],[3495,3566,"Not easy?"],[3582,3674,"You have to pass"],[3674,3828,"The Crucible's highest test."],[4054,4183,"The Ascension Gauntlet."],[4304,4412,"The Ascension Gauntlet?"],[4425,4458,"It's hidden"],[4458,4642,"in the Crucible's private facility."],[4658,4808,"And it's built only for one thing."],[4838,4942,"To push your body"],[4942,5163,"past every human limit."],[5163,5317,"No fighter in the modern-era"],[5317,5401,"has ever cracked it."],[5417,5626,"But if you do, you walk out different."],[5647,5793,"Godweight fully unlocked."],[5809,6072,"You survive, you'll bury Black Tide."],[6101,6218,"You'll bury anyone."],[6239,6381,"Tomorrow, head over to the Crucible."],[6418,6523,"You're the Director now."],[6573,6660,"The gym's yours."],[6681,6744,"All of it."],[6773,6886,"The resources, the staff,"],[6886,6990,"tech, everything."],[7011,7111,"Don't get polite about it."],[7132,7203,"You call the shots."],[7203,7298,"You take what you need."],[7303,7378,"You earn the crown"],[7378,7482,"that you're already wearing."],[7494,7578,"Whatever it takes."],[7603,7736,"As long as it helps me save my mom."],[7766,7816,"Good."],[7882,7978,"Because it's gonna be hell."]],"40":[[809,1030,"The Ascension Chamber is simple."],[1067,1322,"The gases attack your bones, muscles,"],[1322,1409,"and nerves."],[1438,1605,"They rewrite you from the inside out."],[1672,1864,"Most people pass out in 30 seconds."],[1893,2131,"And some, never wake up."],[2202,2327,"But if you fight through it,"],[2377,2448,"you'll wake up"],[2502,2673,"a brand new goddamn brain."],[2781,2873,"Let's fucking go."],[2940,2986,"Okay."],[3128,3207,"Good luck, Director."],[4804,4863,"It's going to kill you."],[4863,4967,"I need to shut this thing down."],[4967,5084,"No!"],[5672,5818,"Holy shit."]],"41":[[304,442,"Holy shit."],[1476,1639,"Hit me as hard as you fucking can."],[3040,3107,"Jesus."],[3232,3411,"It's like 30 percent of what you have now."],[3486,3624,"I can't imagine what the rest looks like."],[3687,3757,"Let's move."]],"42":[[112,371,"Tomorrow is not just another fight."],[387,646,"Tomorrow decides just who we are."],[734,867,"The Black Tide's been trying"],[867,1063,"to destroy everything we built."],[1230,1322,"We can't let that happen."],[1547,1622,"You're the one"],[1622,1776,"who can bring redemption back"],[1776,1851,"to the Crucible."],[1864,1956,"For the rest of you,"],[1985,2206,"protect the Carter Clan."],[2264,2339,"Jax's got it."],[2815,2911,"Crucible!"],[2932,3028,"Crucible!"],[3036,3132,"Crucible!"],[3140,3236,"Crucible!"],[3240,3328,"Crucible!"],[3328,3386,"Let's go!"],[3386,3474,"Fucking Crucible!"],[3582,3870,"Tomorrow, on our own turf,"],[3928,4141,"we're gonna stop the Carter Clan"],[4158,4308,"right out of existence!"],[4421,4579,"Tomorrow, we're gonna"],[4579,4825,"make the Crucible eat dirt!"],[5075,5359,"Tomorrow, Black Tide"],[5380,5605,"owns this country!"],[5935,6089,"And Maria..."],[6381,6502,"You get to watch"],[6502,6748,"every glorious second"],[6823,7073,"as we put the Carter Clan fighters,"],[7073,7215,"one by one"],[7215,7349,"into the ground!"]],"43":[[58,187,"Jax is your grandson."],[225,296,"You can't."],[296,454,"Jax wouldn't even be here."],[467,600,"He wouldn't even exist"],[600,825,"if you hadn't run away 20 years ago."],[825,1017,"None of this would be happening."],[1722,1881,"These are the latest stacks."],[1897,1956,"One shot,"],[1956,2202,"you're 10 times stronger, faster,"],[2202,2431,"meaner, unstoppable."],[2473,2598,"Let's start the trials."],[2598,2740,"I'm done playing fair."],[2777,2840,"I'll go first!"],[2861,2915,"Yeah!"],[2915,3048,"OG Black Tide only."],[4671,4733,"Yes!"],[4792,4871,"Yes!"],[4934,5013,"Yes!"],[5897,6135,"Oh, I feel fucking great!"],[6389,6514,"Now things are going to get"],[6535,6706,"really fucking interesting."],[6756,6927,"Let's tear them apart."],[7086,7148,"Let's go!"],[7665,7753,"Let's get it!"],[7753,7816,"Yeah!"],[7849,8020,"Black Tide!"],[8166,8229,"Yes!"],[8241,8345,"Let's get it!"],[8345,8408,"Yes."],[8508,8612,"Black Tide."]],"44":[[33,150,"Ladies and gentlemen."],[162,404,"Today, we have Black Tide"],[404,558,"against the Crucible."],[579,746,"The East versus the West."],[767,1021,"And today, the winner takes it all!"],[1034,1167,"Let's witness the show!"],[1238,1322,"Hey, Hud."],[1388,1476,"I thought I told you"],[1476,1659,"to bring all the Carter Clan."],[1689,1839,"Competition hasn't started yet."],[1876,2027,"Keep that loud mouth of yours shut."],[2093,2231,"You'll need it later to beg."],[2531,2640,"Two weeks ago,"],[2640,2882,"my fighters kicked all your asses"],[2902,3040,"without even trying."],[3090,3140,"What do you think"],[3140,3253,"is going to happen today"],[3253,3407,"when they really turn it on?"],[3528,3670,"You're going to wish you stayed home,"],[3707,3828,"you little bastard."],[4254,4454,"Let's up the wagers before we even start."],[4871,5000,"If you've got the guts."]],"45":[[108,233,"Whoever loses today"],[271,400,"shuts down their gym."],[429,692,"No rebranding, no rebuilding."],[734,909,"You operate under the winner's banner."],[934,1084,"We end this coastal war for good."],[1172,1284,"Are you sure about that?"],[1322,1463,"You want to gamble everything?"],[1501,1743,"Willing to bet it all on some bastard kid?"],[1785,1922,"Everything that's wrong"],[1976,2143,"started with us and Black Tide."],[2173,2323,"If we become one gym,"],[2398,2519,"bullshit stops."],[2731,2840,"Alright, alright."],[2898,3019,"You are on."],[3023,3207,"But you're gonna regret today forever."],[3240,3382,"Letting Jax Carter"],[3382,3645,"lead the Crucible into destruction."],[3691,3766,"Why wait?"],[3883,4004,"Come on, golden boy!"],[4041,4183,"Let's finish it right here!"],[4300,4375,"You wanna fight?"],[4416,4500,"Fight me first."],[4567,4654,"You serious?"],[4679,4779,"Ryder just beat your"],[4779,4959,"weakling Director's bum ass!"],[5067,5176,"If he's the best you got,"],[5238,5380,"what the hell are you gonna do?"],[5451,5509,"My best."]],"46":[[83,171,"This is it, man."],[171,221,"Come on."],[350,392,"Yes!"],[400,467,"Yeah!"],[483,571,"I'm gonna get you. -Yeah!"],[621,671,"Get it."],[821,896,"Let's go!"],[896,971,"Wait, wait, wait."],[971,1055,"Wait, wait!"],[1121,1197,"Look closer."],[1226,1305,"His veins."],[1343,1422,"His skin."],[1422,1480,"His lips."],[1493,1551,"They're wrong."],[1572,1651,"Looks like they pumped him"],[1651,1705,"with something."],[1764,1826,"Temporary."],[1826,1906,"Synthetic."],[1906,2010,"It's too dangerous in there."],[2093,2168,"Dixxon!"],[2189,2260,"Come on!"],[2781,2857,"Fuck yeah!"],[2961,3048,"Yeah!"],[3737,3849,"That's my boy."],[3924,4029,"Too afraid to step up?"],[4129,4270,"Typical Crucible shit!"]],"47":[[250,350,"What the hell's going on?"],[350,521,"Why's your boy so juiced up like that?"],[550,638,"Does it matter?"],[650,763,"You're not walking out of here"],[763,875,"with a win today."],[992,1042,"No."],[1126,1205,"We can win."],[1292,1388,"If I fight."],[1664,1856,"A former director"],[1901,2018,"is gonna crawl in"],[2035,2173,"against a student?"],[2489,2581,"Shit, old man."],[2602,2715,"You're gonna lose."],[2731,2786,"You might as well"],[2786,2952,"torch the Crucible yourself."],[3361,3465,"Come on now, gramps."],[3507,3699,"Let's see if this fossil still has teeth."]],"48":[[1130,1197,"Come on!"],[2239,2348,"Wait, something's not right."],[2389,2515,"It's like he's juiced up the gills."],[2548,2744,"Bro, if a student's making Hud"],[2744,2840,"fight for his life,"],[2886,2969,"something's way off."],[3503,3649,"Yeah!"],[3716,3837,"Yeah!"],[3837,3920,"Let's fucking go!"],[3920,3995,"Yeah!"],[3995,4095,"Let's fucking go."],[4120,4300,"Save yourself some embarrassment."],[4337,4433,"Get up now,"],[4471,4637,"while you still have some teeth left."],[4654,4742,"You're done!"],[4742,4929,"New era starts today, boys!"],[4954,5142,"Black Tide runs this shit out!"],[5213,5330,"Let's go!"],[5330,5476,"Black Tide!"],[5747,5818,"Yeah!"],[5818,5935,"Black Tide!"],[5964,6097,"Black Tide!"],[6331,6414,"You serious?"],[6431,6573,"You just dropped your former director."],[6610,6723,"Now you wanna be next?"],[6773,6902,"I just wanna see what you're made of."]],"49":[[25,171,"What's the matter, Jax?"],[171,316,"You forget that Black Tide"],[316,596,"just wrecked you like two weeks ago?"],[804,921,"You didn't get stronger."],[975,1046,"But I did."],[1209,1301,"I'll let you win"],[1376,1530,"if you lick my shoes."],[1793,1910,"You really think he can take him?"],[2306,2377,"Let's go!"],[2377,2485,"End this clown!"],[2510,2594,"Come on, Jax!"],[2594,2665,"You got this!"],[2665,2723,"Shut up!"],[2736,2927,"Just watch your little bastard die."],[3895,3953,"Gotcha."]],"50":[[120,312,"What the hell did you pump him full of?"],[354,471,"It's not what you think."],[492,588,"But believe me,"],[613,738,"there's more where that came from."],[817,1063,"If you're curious, come find out."],[1134,1238,"You got lucky!"],[1267,1380,"You think you're hot shit?"],[1447,1501,"Go!"],[1730,1960,"I remember you said I'd win..."],[2093,2231,"if I survive one strike."],[2248,2427,"Yeah, and it still stands."],[2502,2560,"Good."],[2648,2719,"Same with you."],[3511,3591,"One strike."],[3691,3770,"You lose."]],"51":[[0,75,"One strike."],[183,241,"You lose."],[266,325,"Bastard."],[412,533,"This isn't real."],[571,663,"I'm supposed to be"],[663,821,"ten times stronger than you!"],[825,967,"No way."],[1042,1155,"He beat both of them"],[1226,1530,"without barely any effort."],[1559,1634,"Is this what they mean"],[1634,1755,"by Godweight Build?"],[1822,1901,"Amazing."],[1989,2143,"The kid's got real talent."],[2348,2544,"Good thing they call me the Talent Killer."],[2798,2902,"Go get him, Taggert."],[2957,3044,"You old fuck,"],[3044,3153,"you don't know when to quit."],[3232,3303,"Heads up,"],[3319,3428,"he's coming for your throat."],[3449,3607,"Game over, little bastard!"],[3628,3741,"You're dead meat now!"],[4033,4124,"Why do you want me dead"],[4124,4225,"so bad, Taggert?"],[4250,4496,"Because looking at you reminds me of"],[4496,4637,"what they did to my daughter."],[5830,5935,"You're mine."]],"52":[[1046,1155,"Not bad, kid."],[1217,1355,"It's rare anyone survives"],[1355,1463,"my first flurry."],[1547,1634,"Let's see..."],[1822,1968,"if you survive this."],[2185,2268,"Oh shit!"],[2268,2352,"Stack pill."],[2364,2427,"Supercharge."],[2427,2519,"It's a death wish."],[2915,3090,"You're a dead man, Carter!"],[3595,3674,"Jax!"],[3737,3866,"Crush him, Coach!"],[3866,3983,"Show that little bastard"],[3983,4079,"what real power is!"],[4079,4300,"Should've stayed home, Carter Clan!"],[4379,4437,"Get up!"],[4462,4650,"Get up!"],[4959,5075,"Jax!"],[5326,5513,"Get up!"],[6810,6923,"What's he doing?"],[6923,7198,"It's like the air is warping around him."]],"53":[[25,191,"That kind of strength and power."],[254,425,"You can't shoot in your veins."],[546,692,"That's the Godweight Build."],[704,800,"Bullshit."],[800,896,"That's a myth."],[896,1013,"A damn legend."],[1013,1151,"No one really has it."],[1192,1247,"No."],[1351,1422,"It's true."],[1539,1647,"I just tasted it."],[1726,1805,"And now,"],[1851,1972,"I want more!"],[2064,2135,"Come on!"],[3303,3382,"Did you see that?"],[3465,3566,"That's not human."],[3566,3611,"That's..."],[3691,3807,"That's a god."],[3941,3999,"Fuck it."],[4258,4483,"You forced my hand!"],[7557,7665,"Jax, stop!"]],"54":[[4,108,"Jax, stop!"],[246,379,"He's your grandfather."],[558,917,"I thought I was invincible."],[1026,1130,"I'd never lose."],[1226,1564,"Especially to a punk kid like you, Jax."],[1630,1722,"But you beat me."],[1847,1972,"You beat me fair and square."],[2160,2306,"No, no, no, no, no, no!"],[2310,2398,"Shoot me up!"],[2398,2460,"Twice!"],[2485,2569,"Let me fight!"],[2585,2656,"Let me fight!"],[2656,2711,"Come on!"],[2711,2831,"Silence, boy!"],[2952,2982,"No!"],[2982,3044,"It's over."],[3257,3336,"It's over."],[3820,3958,"Wooh!"],[4041,4179,"Yeah!"],[4179,4316,"He got him."],[4316,4375,"Nice."],[4400,4517,"Dude, yes."],[4808,4871,"We did it."],[4871,5017,"You got a good kid, Maria."],[5067,5163,"A real good kid."],[5271,5355,"We are honorable."],[5472,5605,"Black Tide is finished."],[5651,5743,"From now on,"],[5789,5918,"we ride or die"],[5980,6135,"under the Crucible banner."],[6539,6660,"Thank you, Dad."],[6710,6835,"Don't thank me, Maria."],[6948,7136,"Just do a better job raising him"],[7290,7478,"than I did with you."]],"55":[[50,229,"That bastard ruined us."],[271,475,"Carter Clan, the Crucible,"],[504,725,"and now Black Tide too?"],[825,938,"He's not human."],[971,1205,"And no way one kid does all this."],[1222,1347,"Oh, we gotta find a way."],[1739,1910,"There is one way."],[1989,2127,"The Godweight Build,"],[2156,2218,"it's real."],[2268,2439,"But I've been working on something."],[2565,2648,"What is it?"],[2702,2827,"I'll show you."],[2869,3036,"I call it Prime Drive."],[3069,3174,"Synthesized from"],[3174,3332,"nasty-ass compounds."],[3365,3440,"Designed to recreate"],[3440,3641,"the effects of the Godweight Build"],[3641,3728,"and then some."],[3837,3995,"But I've only tested it on rats."],[4074,4162,"They exploded."],[4162,4237,"I don't care."],[4354,4517,"Jax Carter humiliated me."],[4600,4779,"Cost me my shot at the Crucible."],[4833,4979,"Cost me everything."],[5021,5142,"Everything!"],[5259,5388,"Whatever this thing does,"],[5568,5672,"I'll survive it."],[5759,5830,"And then,"],[5889,6089,"I'm gonna destroy him!"]],"56":[[154,225,"You changed everything,"],[225,300,"Director Jax."],[337,467,"We'll hold down the fort till you're back."],[575,663,"Thanks for everything, Hud."],[1480,1572,"This hasn't been tested"],[1572,1668,"on any human."],[1676,1764,"Stick it in!"],[2977,3516,"I feel untouchable!"],[3770,3920,"Fuck! - Yeah!"],[4029,4108,"Wooh!"],[4108,4179,"Yeah!"],[4925,4996,"That power,"],[4996,5117,"it's not stable."],[5117,5255,"You're not stable."],[5388,5526,"That's the point."],[7090,7236,"Nobody gets it."],[7315,7507,"Just me."]],"57":[[996,1209,"Where's Jax?"],[1664,1747,"Wrong answer."],[5255,5313,"No!"],[7311,7382,"No!"],[8320,8383,"Dad!"]],"58":[[1096,1192,"Don't worry."],[1384,1518,"You get to live"],[1555,1693,"for just long enough"],[1810,2031,"to deliver Jax a message."],[2147,2385,"Tell him, I'll be waiting"],[2410,2569,"at the combine."],[2610,2698,"Tonight."],[2798,2890,"Re-match!"]],"59":[[675,734,"Troy!"],[809,892,"What happened?"],[1092,1363,"Dante came for you."],[1422,1689,"He took Camden and Blake,"],[1714,1797,"he said"],[1835,1939,"to meet him"],[2060,2243,"at the Black Tide combine"],[2369,2435,"tonight."],[2669,2777,"We're getting you to the hospital."],[2794,2869,"No point."],[2986,3078,"I'm not gonna make it."],[3837,3999,"I treated you like garbage, man."],[4183,4275,"Your mom, too."],[4654,4733,"I was wrong."],[4954,5030,"I'm sorry."],[6377,6477,"I swear to you,"],[6715,6819,"he's gonna pay for this."]],"60":[[437,533,"Guess what, fellas?"],[600,779,"We killed Troy and Frank."],[842,1013,"You guys are just basically bait."],[1063,1180,"When Jax gets here,"],[1297,1368,"game over."],[1384,1601,"You are not laying your hand on him."],[1685,1851,"Jax is mine."],[1897,2147,"He's all mine."],[2185,2298,"Fine by me, son."],[3315,3420,"That's enough!"],[5030,5105,"Be careful."],[5176,5342,"Something's changed in Dante."],[5384,5622,"Something's changed alright."],[5793,5860,"Round two."],[6043,6185,"Winner takes all."]],"61":[[963,1151,"Still protecting the same family"],[1151,1309,"that treated you like scum?"],[1351,1647,"You side with them, you die with them."],[1793,2010,"You forget, Taggert is my dad."],[5526,5668,"Time to go help Jax."]],"62":[[1309,1401,"What the hell are you on?"],[1468,1551,"Prime Drive."],[1605,1722,"I'm not just strong."],[1789,1985,"I'm unstoppable!"],[2260,2373,"I'll be the judge of that."],[2973,3211,"Jax isn't the same kid from the gym."],[7011,7102,"Godweight Build?"],[7178,7349,"Don't seem too godly for me."]],"63":[[738,863,"Time to die together."],[975,1088,"Family style."],[1351,1434,"He's too strong."],[1472,1630,"I've never seen anything like it."],[1764,1835,"I'll distract him."],[1835,1910,"You go for his eyes."],[2081,2394,"Try me, motherfucker."],[4421,4542,"Ah, my eyes!"],[4600,4725,"My eyes!"],[4758,4863,"I'm gonna kill you."],[4904,5034,"I'm gonna fucking kill you."],[5626,5751,"It's time to end this."]],"64":[[321,446,"You killed my uncle."],[504,617,"You killed Troy."],[721,834,"You deserve this."],[867,971,"They deserved it."],[1021,1117,"You all do."],[1372,1468,"You bastard."],[1518,1751,"You fucking useless bastard!"],[1876,2035,"Killing you would be too easy."],[2106,2189,"You're gonna live."],[2223,2314,"Live with all of it."],[2348,2435,"Your gym's gone."],[2489,2606,"Your power's gone."],[2694,2848,"Regret's the only thing you got left."],[3132,3269,"That's what I want you living with."]],"65":[[688,863,"So Frank and Troy,"],[934,1092,"they really did some damage."],[1176,1480,"To you, her, to all of us."],[1576,1764,"They used to be part of this family."],[1822,1922,"But not anymore."],[2135,2281,"Forgiving doesn't mean forgetting."],[2519,2673,"It just means we're ready to move on."],[3094,3174,"I'm sorry."],[3228,3432,"So sorry for what I did to you back then."],[3478,3578,"Dismissing you."],[3624,3720,"Disowning you."],[4033,4412,"I really, really failed you."],[4642,4733,"You didn't fail me."],[4821,4975,"You gave me a safe place to live."],[5088,5188,"You gave me a son."],[5822,5960,"That's more than I had before."],[6197,6310,"Son."],[6740,7161,"Do, do you think that there'll be a day"],[7236,7307,"when you could"],[7674,7916,"consider calling me Dad?"],[8692,8737,"Maybe."],[9180,9250,"If you earn it."],[9763,9847,"Come here."],[11040,11177,"They called me bastard."],[11240,11357,"Said I didn't belong."],[11448,11649,"But I turned that name into a title."],[11703,11790,"This family."],[11840,11932,"This legacy?"],[12012,12124,"It's mine now."],[12195,12433,"I'm The Bastard King."]]}